','Em 1966, na França, Jean Desjoyaux construiu sua primeira piscina com a ideia de que a sua família pudesse aproveitar momentos de alegria na própria casa. É com essa visão que a Desjoyaux começou a desenvolver a sua tecnologia própria, se tornando sinônimo de qualidade, tecnologia e tranquilidade com a invenção de conceitos exclusivos que revolucionaram o mundo da piscina'),(56,5,'_options_history_history_content','field_options_home_options_history_history_content'),(57,5,'options_history_history_years_0_history_year','1966'),(58,5,'_options_history_history_years_0_history_year','field_options_home_options_history_history_years_history_year'),(59,5,'options_history_history_years_0_history_image','13'),(60,5,'_options_history_history_years_0_history_image','field_options_home_options_history_history_years_history_image'),(61,5,'options_history_history_years_0_hitory_year_title','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur'),(62,5,'_options_history_history_years_0_hitory_year_title','field_options_home_options_history_history_years_hitory_year_title'),(63,5,'options_history_history_years_0_hitory_year_content','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Mauris ultrices tortor'),(64,5,'_options_history_history_years_0_hitory_year_content','field_options_home_options_history_history_years_hitory_year_content'),(65,5,'options_history_history_years','4'),(66,5,'_options_history_history_years','field_options_home_options_history_history_years'),(67,5,'options_history_history_content_footer','Juntos, tornamos a piscina dos seus sonhos realidade!'),(68,5,'_options_history_history_content_footer','field_options_home_options_history_history_content_footer'),(69,5,'options_history',''),(70,5,'_options_history','field_options_home_options_history'),(71,5,'options_why_why_title','PORQUE A DESJOYAUX'),(72,5,'_options_why_why_title','field_options_home_options_why_why_title'),(73,5,'options_why_why_subtitle','Bem-Vindos ao que há de mais moderno no mundo das piscinas!'),(74,5,'_options