amília desde 1966'),(1020,31,'_options_history_history_subtitle','field_home_options_history_history_subtitle'),(1021,31,'options_history_history_content','Em 1966, na França, Jean Desjoyaux construiu sua primeira piscina com a ideia de que a sua família pudesse aproveitar momentos de alegria na própria casa. É com essa visão que a Desjoyaux começou a desenvolver a sua tecnologia própria, se tornando sinônimo de qualidade, tecnologia e tranquilidade com a invenção de conceitos exclusivos que revolucionaram o mundo da piscina'),(1022,31,'_options_history_history_content','field_home_options_history_history_content'),(1023,31,'options_history_history_years_0_history_year','1966'),(1024,31,'_options_history_history_years_0_history_year','field_home_options_history_history_years_history_year'),(1025,31,'options_history_history_years_0_history_image','13'),(1026,31,'_options_history_history_years_0_history_image','field_home_options_history_history_years_history_image'),(1027,31,'options_history_history_years_0_hitory_year_title','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur'),(1028,31,'_options_history_history_years_0_hitory_year_title','field_home_options_history_history_years_hitory_year_title'),(1029,31,'options_history_history_years_0_hitory_year_content','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Mauris ultrices tortor'),(1030,31,'_options_history_history_years_0_hitory_year_content','field_home_options_history_history_years_hitory_year_content'),(1031,31,'options_history_history_years','2'),(1032,31,'_options_history_history_years','field_home_options_history_history_years'),(1033,31,'options_history_history_content_footer','Juntos, tornamos a piscina dos seus sonhos realidade!'),(1034,31,'_options_history_history_content_footer','field_home_options_history_history_content_footer'),(1035,31,'options_history',''),(1036,31,'_options_history','field_home_options_history'),(1037,31,'options_why_why_title','PORQUE A DESJOYAUX'),(1038,31,'_options_why_why_title','field_home_opt